                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17970111-14-off84 t17970111-14-cd85"></join>, three quart bottles, value 3d. a quart of brandy, value 3s. a quart pewter pot, value 1s. 6d. a quart of gin, value 2s. a yard of canvas, value 1s. and two glass bottles, value 2d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
